{"tid":2462744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片丨陳奕迅同adidas割席後首現身 獨坐車廂發呆成粒鐘","createTime":"2021-03-26T07:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T07:54:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"544a2834854df433680bda81d1ce05e3eb339e8f","tid":2462744,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"Eason昨晚發割席聲明後首度現身，有《蘋果》讀者目睹Eason獨自在車上發呆成粒鐘，未知是否被網民留鬧爆所影響。Eason昨晚6時35分發聲明，讀者洪先生於個半鐘後發現他在中環荷李活道出現，洪先生透過「爆相爆片」報料說：「我噚晚（25日）8點左右，見佢一個人揸住部車泊咗喺荷李活道，我同個朋友一齊，我朋友係佢fans，諗住等佢落車之後問吓佢可唔可以合照，點知佢喺車度成個鐘都冇落車，我就同朋友走咗冇再等。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210326/RNK4TOAGRFHGFIBRHI6PQTXC3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210326%2FRNK4TOAGRFHGFIBRHI6PQTXC3E%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=8c51864e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210326%2FRNK4TOAGRFHGFIBRHI6PQTXC3E%2F&h=e399770f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210326/RNK4TOAGRFHGFIBRHI6PQTXC3E/</a>"},{"pid":"d4a19f68956067faaf827fcc598e55618de56f1a","tid":2462744,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"有錢人的生活 往往就是這麼樸實無華且枯燥"},{"pid":"46c0c00c08fae1e7fda237d6398e1f4142f3728e","tid":2462744,"uid":80243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔撚洗扮野啦，扮撚晒身不由己"},{"pid":"d1c36d3fb73cf8649603996c87431a07d9f7f809","tid":2462744,"uid":292601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"佢數緊棉花(人仔）姐"},{"pid":"2f73d3b4da036d932f48dd0604b457385836caca","tid":2462744,"uid":263183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"唔想番屋企對住老婆"},{"pid":"2a3ec4f059d436f78aab42aee970c2700d75b54f","tid":2462744,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"